      "description": "Step into luxury with this absolutely pristine vehicle! It is in truly mint condition, looking and driving just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. Every detail has been meticulously cared for, from the flawless exterior to the spotless interior. This is a rare find for a buyer who demands perfection and a like-new driving experience!",
