    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride in ownership, presenting in excellent overall condition. The exterior retains a deep, reflective shine across all panels, with only a few minor stone chips on the front fascia that are typical of careful road use. The alloy wheels are clean and free of significant curbing. Inside, the cabin feels fresh and well-preserved; the premium leather seating is supple with no rips or thinning, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. Every electronic component, from the heated seats to the intuitive infotainment system, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is robust and ready for the road. It has a documented service history, with a recent oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection already completed. The engine runs quietly and delivers smooth power, while the transmission provides seamless shifts. This is a turn-key vehicle that offers a premium driving experience without the 'new car' price tag.",
